Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.84,Default,All,0,0,0,,Hitotsu hegi hegi ni hegigoshi hachikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.73,Default,All,0,0,0,,Bongame, bongome, bongomou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.35,Default,All,0,0,0,,Tsumitate tsumi mame tsumi sanshou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Choshadan no chashoujyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:23.49,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okome no namagami. Ohome no namakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.64,Default,All,0,0,0,,Konkogome no namakakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.65,Default,All,0,0,0,,Shusu. Hisuzu. Shusu. Shuchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.78,Default,All,0,0,0,,Oya mo kahei. Ko mo kahei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:33.02,Default,All,0,0,0,,Oyakahei, kokahei. Kokahei, oyakahei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.14,Default,All,0,0,0,,Furu kuri no furu kirikuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Amagappa. Kabangappaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.08,Default,All,0,0,0,,Kisama no kyahan mo kawagihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.34,Default,All,0,0,0,,Shikka bakama no shippo korobi wo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:43.53,Default,All,0,0,0,,Minna de tabinaga ni chotto muite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:47.79,Default,All,0,0,0,,Mudo soto sono nakade kawara sekiniko sekichiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:51.34,Default,All,0,0,0,,Nora nyorai. Nora nyorai. Mina nyorai. Munora nyorai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:54.52,Default,All,0,0,0,,Choto saki no okoho botoke ni okesu na okyaku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.27,Default,All,0,0,0,,Hosonaga ni, hosodomo ni, hosonoyo ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:59.33,Default,All,0,0,0,,Kyou mo nama nama nara nara nama no mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:03.73,Default,All,0,0,0,,Choto shiokande, ochato chatacho chatto chotato chotecho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:06.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Aoda tokasen de hochacha tochaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.31,Default,All,0,0,0,,Koo ha koo de moo ni koo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:10.79,Default,All,0,0,0,,Kouya no yama no okera kozou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.79,Default,All,0,0,0,,Tanuki hyappiki, ashi hyakuzen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.19,Default,All,0,0,0,,Tenmoku hyappai, bou happyappon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:17.80,Default,All,0,0,0,,Bugubagu bugubagu, nibugubagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.67,Default,All,0,0,0,,Awasete bugubagu, mugububagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.40,Default,All,0,0,0,,Kikukuri kikukuri, miki kukuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:24.66,Default,All,0,0,0,,Awasete kikukuri muki kukuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:27.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Mugi gomi mugi gomi nimugi gomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:29.40,Default,All,0,0,0,,Awasete mugigomi mumugi gomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:33.71,Default,All,0,0,0,,Ano nageshino no nage naginata ha dada nagenawa no fuhou no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:43.52,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,This is so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm feel like I'm going to bite my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:59.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What are these long ass sentences about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man Koumura gave them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They're supposed to help us\Npractice vocalization and articulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop chatting and join back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, are you making progress with the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:14.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm writing a little at a time as I remember the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:17.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think I can finish it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ryou and Kotomi will do Sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Youhei and I will do Lighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya can do Effects and Directing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, and I'll be the actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.82,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's starting to look more and more like a drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:33.15,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,There are still so many things we need to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.72,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Like the costume and music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.93,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,What should we do about the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Anyone good with sewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I guess I could give it a shot, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm not confident in mine, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then that leaves…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.84,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 21
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.84,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}In Preparation for the School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.88,San,San,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See? It was a good call to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But Mom's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.07,San,San,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll work on it a little here and there as I find the time between work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone else who can possibly do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, but still…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:15.30,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So you're back, my daughter\Nwho carries my superb genes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…plus one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you calling “plus one”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Hey, I rented a good thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:22.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.04,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, where is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.48,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.68,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Look at this gorgeous view!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,How splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:36.18,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's a world fitting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A video of a play, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks like it'll be a good reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I've never seen a theatrical play, so this really helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've never seen a play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:52.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I didn't even get the chance to watch\Nan elementary school play since I was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yet another bomb dropped by the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't research while crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, I'm really touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I never knew drama was this amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:25.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Compared to this, mine's like child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:28.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So what if it's child's play?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you put your heart into it, people will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What's this? You were flirting with Nagisa this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We were watching the video you got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Perfect timing. Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You were looking for something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Operation Potty-Chair starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you we're not looking for a potty-chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.38,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Are you sure this picture or children's book\Nyou were looking for is hidden in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It might be a theatrical play after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:19.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's possible that Nagisa saw\Na play in the past and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:27.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If she'd seen something\Nlike that, I'd definitely know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Since I don't recall anything like that, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:36.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:37.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No, this isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's the potty-chair Nagisa used to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you so hung up on the potty-chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You moron! I didn't find it because I was looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:03.59,San,San,0,0,0,,Both of you, please keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.79,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Look, she yelled at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're saying it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:17.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I got a great idea from watching the video!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A song! If we insert a song at the climax, I'm sure it'll be very exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can sing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've only sung in music classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I think it'll become really good if we insert a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not denying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:41.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But, maybe you shouldn't worry too much about making the play a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:47.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not a big production play, so do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since it's a stage you made for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A stage I made…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right, and I want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think that's what counts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:07.15,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This is a world that has ended. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A world where no one exists aside from myself. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:14.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,In the room is a small table and a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Beyond the window is a barren and expansive plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Is this interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I think it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,We conducted some research, \Nbut couldn't discover the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The story isn't complete yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.40,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So, do you know any music that'll fit well as BGM?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.48,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rie-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.30,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,I have a picture in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.40,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,All you have to do is put yourself in the girl's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the girl's shoes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:52.40,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,It's not about being alone at school or home,\Nbut being alone in the world. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.22,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,It's a very sad thing, isn't it? {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a very sad thing. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.82,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Music with a sad tone will probably fit well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.46,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Are all of these CDs yours, Nishina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.47,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Rie-chan loves music, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.26,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.98,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,It's a song called Ma Mère L'Oye by Ravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:28.48,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ma Mère what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.75,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Ma Mère L'Oye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.35,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,It's Mother Goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:37.41,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Since your play has a fantasia-like mood,\NI thought it would fit well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.46,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Ravel composed many fantasia-like pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:45.03,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,This piece was for a Märchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's wonderful! It's surprising how perfectly it fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.22,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.41,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's really lively in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sakagami-san. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.99,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Because my eyes are bad, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But you never wore them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.20,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't like how glasses look on me very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Then how about getting contact lenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.95,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Those are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.73,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.77,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,How are things going here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,As you can see, we're making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But we still have lots to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're only getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.91,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The path we are taking is still continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Let us both keep working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.50,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.11,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,As I thought, you're a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.78,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She's one hell of an underclassman, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll try acting along with the music now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will you watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A room that was once empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But now, there are many people gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:20.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We all share this time together as Nagisa works hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:24.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…so we can share the joy together, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really are amazing, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.39,San,San,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's finally the School Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Get the rehearsal down good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll get it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Today's just practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The real thing is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:38.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've practiced so much that once you're on the stage, your body will move on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're really cute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, can you wait until later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Woah there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's really approaching the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This row is starting to get crooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.24,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Bring some sheets over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.83,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This looks very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.54,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,My hands are getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.92,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Nagisa, don't move, all right?\NOtherwise we won't know the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A little higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:20.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need the light in the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, try turning it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm getting really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I don't think so. This was something my kid asked me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I can't give it to you so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's not something you can find lying around just anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.69,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It gets pretty dark on the side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll need a flashlight tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My heart's pounding really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:51.18,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Relax, relax. Imagine that the seats are\Nfilled with something other than people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What should I think they are, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:57.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,If not people, then how about aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:04.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,They've come to invade the Earth, so they won't care what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't want them to be completely oblivious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want them to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:13.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In that case, your acting determines if the Earth will be invaded or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If you put on a good performance for the aliens, then there'll be no invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But if you give a poor performance, the world gets wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That puts huge pressure on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:27.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, she's really reaching her limit,\Nso quit the idiot talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I'm starting to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:30.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.77,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The drama club is up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:36.96,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.02,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Okay, give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get nervous again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:48.68,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You just said you were calming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:55.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but when I think about\Nhow hard you've all worked for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:01.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or rather, we're all here to make this moment an enjoyable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I… guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The School Festival is run by everyone participating in it, so don't take all the pressure on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.13,Default,PA,0,0,0,,Drama club. If you're ready, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's give this a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.70,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's just something I saw on the TV before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,but we should huddle up, put our hands together, and do a “Let's go!” kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.54,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I saw one of those, too. That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I want to try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right everyone, hands in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:33.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I did this all the time when I was on the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Drama club, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.85,Default,All,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Off you go, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:38.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.61,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Let's all take positions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.16,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.40,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's go, Youhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap, I'm starting to get nervous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Welcome back, the fruit of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,By the way, you're not included.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.86,San,San,0,0,0,,How did the rehearsal go, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well… How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Flawless as usual, like all the other practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.78,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,As expected of our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,By tomorrow, all of the idol agencies will be looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just agree with me, damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san never flatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. That's why you can count on him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.80,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa, can I have your autograph while I have the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What doting parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The same thing will happen to you once you have a daughter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I swear it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can see you having one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,since you are very much like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? Me and him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,My daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Daddy's really shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't say that when I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will you be going to bed soon, Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,May I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:31.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing in particular, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're so nervous you can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'd be more surprised to find that you were sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm a nervous wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's your first stage performance, so it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take the opportunity to get as nervous as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. I will do my very best to get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:09.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The old man and Sanae-san\Nwill be at the performance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:10.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:20.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's just that I realized how much\NI'm loved by Dad and Mom again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure. It's hard to find parents like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:28.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I still can't stop thinking about\Nwhat happened when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The thing where you feel like you've done something bad to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:35.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Because of what Nagisa would probably think. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:43.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That because of her, Sanae and I\Nhad to give up on our dreams. {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:47.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're being overly sensitive about all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have a habit of thinking you're at fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,so this is just your imagination, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need to concentrate on\Ntomorrow's performance right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think about other stuff after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good night, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:18.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't forget anything for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:26.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Costume…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Towel…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,These pictures…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I found some old albums and diaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, I never knew about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I never knew Dad used to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:10.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It seems like… they both gave up on their dreams for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, don't think about any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need to give your body a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need to get some sleep, even if it's only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:42.64,San,San,0,0,0,,After picking Nagisa up at kindergarten, we took a stroll to the river bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:46.14,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm really happy to be able to be with Nagisa every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:52.99,San,San,0,0,0,,If I had continued to work as a teacher, I don't think I would have been able to experience this joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:57.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.74,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What a mess…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is the worst time for her to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn it.
