Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:45.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The two people in the pictures looked like they were enjoying their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:48.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Of course they were,\Nsince they were living out their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:52.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And it was supposed to last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Besides, they're enjoying their lives right now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.72,0:23:58.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But they gave up on their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:00.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:08.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And right now, I'm trying to live out\Nmy own dream after sacrificing theirs.
